  "detailed_description": "The beasts are back in Mutant Fighting Cup 2! BIGGER! BETTER! MORE FEARSOME THAN EVER! Evolve, mutate and train your monsters to win the monster championship in hard brutal turn-based strategy battles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/561450/extras/e0855e95c0059d3a736520a682edb6b6.avif?t=1572367839\" width=621 height=230 /></span><br>- FIGHT! Take on monstrous opponents and powerful bosses across the globe!<br>- TRAIN! Choose your dog, cat, rat or turtle animal and command them in combat!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/561450/extras/596efbaa72c729411767433cd97c1e5e.avif?t=1572367839\" width=621 height=80 /></span><br>- EVOLVE! Use mutant genes to change breed and gain awesome new abilities!<br>- METAMORPHOSIS! Mix and match genes to unlock over 1 million creature combinations!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/561450/extras/5180b06d1a649ee1ce0968e4f5353ff8.avif?t=1572367839\" width=621 height=230 /></span><br>- STRATEGY! Use skills and power ups wisely in extreme RPG tournaments!<br>- PVP! Challenge your friends to player-vs-player multiplayer action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/561450/extras/300d9a58fd8a59b9095b10ffea6c334e.avif?t=1572367839\" width=621 height=230 /></span><br><br>- WIN! Win trophies, achievements and compete with players on the leaderboards!<br>Evolve your monster and win the Mutant Fighting Cup!",
